responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "A78984D449D246591873C59E1BF99B76", "You know, there\'s an old saying from General Varyos: \"When the flame burns too wild, it consumes itself.\" That\'s what the Ashen Flame tribe is looking like to me, a mess waiting to happen. And I don\'t have time to clean up their ashes. I\'m a soldier, not some bureaucrat or silver-tongued diplomat. My blade\'s for battle, not speeches.")
